title: Data Hub Forwarding Agent Input/Output Data and MIM - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
text: Input/Output Data The Data Hub agent expects UDRs of the type selected in the Tables Mapping tab of the selected Data Hub profile. MIM This agent do not publish or access any additional MIM parameters. For information about the MIM and a list of the general MIM parameters, see the Desktop User's Guide .
